FBIS3-32969 "drlat032_o_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 Colombia Government, People's Militia Sign Peace Preagreement PA1502185994 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 1730 GMT 15 Feb 94 PA1502185994 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Report by Sandra Vergara on the "National" newscast] [Text] Good afternoon. At this very moment, in the presence of Fabio Villegas, government and interior minister, the governor of Antioquia Department, the mayor of Medellin, and representatives of the People's Militia, a preagreement for the negotiation of a real peace process between the People's Militia and the Colombian Government is being signed. The members of the People's Militia have said that a cease fire will begin with the signing of this preagreement and that in the next 30 days, approximately 400 armed militiamen will surrender their weapons.
